ADDER       Position adder
    INPA            Position input A
    INPB            Position input B
    INPC            Position input C
    INPD            Position input D
    INPA_INVERT     Sign invert input A
    INPB_INVERT     Sign invert input B
    INPC_INVERT     Sign invert input C
    INPD_INVERT     Sign invert input D
    SCALE           Scale divisor after add
    OUT             Position output
